Aloha by Blissful Ganges
Step into the tranquility of these beautifully furnished apartments, situated in Tapovan, Rishikesh, Uttarakhand, India. Nestled within the prestigious “Aloha on the Ganges” resort, experience a serene escape by the blissful Ganges. Enjoy the luxury and comfort of these inviting accommodations, surrounded by nature’s beauty, for an unforgettable stay.
Privately Owned) in Rishikesh! Our premium accommodations are designed to provide you with a truly blissful experience. Enjoy a range of facilities, including a seasonal outdoor infinity swimming pool, a tranquil garden, a badminton court, shared lounge cum Club to enjoy indoor games, and rejuvenating spa. Stay connected with free WiFi in your room and take advantage of private parking on-site. Aloha Resort boasts a mesmerising three-side river view, offering a serene atmosphere for your stay.
